message.text:
for me, joining feucso was one of the best decisions i've ever made. back then, before i entered college i told myself na i'd join creatives and hone my skills sa graphic design. years later, creatives director na ako ng feucso :)) under this org i have grown a lot not only sa skills sa pag edit, but as a student leader as well.

aside from work, i made a lot of friends whom i cherish a lot and i can say na super welcoming ng environment here. grabe din yung room for growth. even if medyo nakakabaliw din ang revisions and sunod sunod na pubs (di tlg siya maiiwasan), at the end of the day  meron parin ng  sense of fulfillment na nagagawa mo yung something you love while also being able to serve the student body.

feucso became my stepping stone sa pag grow both as a graphic artist (?? wow) and as a student leader. i'm really glad that i took that leap of faith back then. i hope u guys would consider joining feucso (creatives HEHEHEHE) and experience the same thing i did — or even better than mine.

p.s: typo godz tlg creatives ... sorry .... 

you may submit your application here:
https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

APPLY NAAAA RAAAAAHH

Hello everyone! 💚✨

I need a little help and support today 🥺 Currently, I still have 5 kitti tubs left — Banana Pudding 🍌 and Tiramisu 🍰 — and I’d love for you to enjoy them before they’re all gone!

Also we have been recognized by supportlocal mnl!!
And its because of all of your support🤍

These are made fresh and are perfect for your cravings, study breaks, or even as a sweet pasalubong for family and friends. 🤎

Every order really means a lot and helps me continue sharing Tamu with all of you. Thank you so much in advance for supporting! 💚
Message me if you’d like to reserve yours. 🙌
